9 An Act relating to higher education; amending 70 O.S.
2021, Section 3206.3, which relates to research and
10 development at institutions of higher education;
directing certain policy established by the Oklahoma
11 State Regents for Higher Education to include certain
tiered system of ownership and require certain
12 compensation; adding area of encouragement for
certain development; requiring certain policies to be
13 reviewed with certain frequency; updating statutory
language; providing an effective date; and declaring
14 an emergency.
15
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3206.3, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 3206.3. A. The Oklahoma State Regents for Higher
21 Education shall:
22 1. Establish, pursuant to the requirements of this paragraph, a
23 model policy, which to the extent not inconsistent with this section
24 may be adapted by the governing board of regents for each
