18 within The Oklahoma State System of Higher Education,
19 its faculty, staff, or students,
20 c. a method to inform the faculty, staff, students, and
21 third parties conducting research on the premises of
22 or with the assistance of the faculty, staff, or
23 students of an institution within The Oklahoma State
